name: Choose our light
description: @nft_and | We do not have the opportunity to choose our time of coming to the world, our race, our country, our gender.  However, it is up to us to choose to be a good and quality human being and to change our environment. Choose your light, it was a work that made me think about these issues.  We were born as human beings and I believe that we have a vision of leaving the world as human beings.
